data.description:
What could be better than this? WALK TO CHICK FIL A!!!!
Check out this adorable 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the popular Lakes Subdivision! Walking distance to both Matilda Harris Elementary School and Camden Middle School! 
Spacious and bright living room- wrap around porch with windows brings extra light into this room! Dining Room and kitchen overlook the oversized screened porch with high ceilings and the fenced in backyard! Shed conveys with home! Grill for the whole family on the extended patio that opens up to the porch and the backdoor to the 2 door attached garage. Primary bedroom and ensuite located on the main level of home. Primary has 2 walk in closets! One traditional and one loops under the stairs! Lots of room for storage! Upstairs is great for kids or for roommates! 2 equal oversized bedrooms with double closets. Bathroom with linen closet in between them! Driveway can park cars side by side easily ! Great for larger families or plenty of space to play basketball! Convenient to Kings Bay Naval Base, 1 miles from I95, 20 minutes to JAX airport, 35 minutes to FLETC- Easy commute to both Jacksonville and Brunswick! 
Don't miss out on seeing this cute home!
